properties.headline: High Wind Warning issued January 17 at 3:50AM MST until January 17 at 8:00PM MST by NWS Albuquerque NM
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 30 to 40 mph with gusts up to 60 mph
expected.

* WHERE...Central Highlands and Northeast Highlands.

* WHEN...From 10 AM this morning to 8 PM MST this evening.

* IMPACTS...High winds may move loose debris, damage property and
cause power outages. Travel will be difficult especially for
high profile vehicles on north to south oriented roads.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...For those driving on I-25 between Bernal,
Las Vegas, and Watrous, expect extreme cross winds. This
includes mile markers 330 through 365.
properties.instruction:
People are urged to secure loose objects that could be blown
around or damaged by the wind.

NWSheadline: HIGH WIND WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 10 AM THIS MORNING TO 8 PM MST THIS EVENING
